@jccardonar Thank you for the feedback! The new release is on its way! ;-)

MIBs are generally rather buggy. We have a workaround which is to fix broken MIBs manually and keeping the compiled versions at http://mibs.snmplabs.com/ where pysnmp could find them automatically.

