With the 2016.0601.0 release, the regular expression used to match the key on each SPEC line was expanded to match the entire key, rather than some part of it.  This was discovered with support for our XPCS instrument (uses #XPCS lines which matched against the standard #X macro for temperature support).

Likely your data files were caught up in this.  Apologies.

Can you send me an example of your SPEC file with MCA data?
Improving support for MCA data is a TODO item.  Need more example data files.

