After weighing the options a little, I don't think we should use `limit` at all. It's not in the docs, and Transfer may consider it a "bug" and remove it down the line. Maybe unlikely, but if we bake assumptions into the SDK those propagate into a potentially large number of clients, so not using it is safer and more conservative.


